<h3>Plagiarism Module</h3>
<p>Use this module to inform students about OSU's plagiarism rules or any other plagiarism information.  </p>
<p>This module contains a rich-text editor that can be used to inform students about plagiarism. Things to add include, but are not limited to: links to OSU's plagiarism rules, information about how to avoid plagiarizing, or a link to the writing center.</p>

