</div>

<p><strong>Tip:</strong> Use your favorite text editor to write longer content, then just cut and paste the text into the area  provided. All your formatting will be preserved.  </p>
<p><strong>Tip:</strong> If this is a module you will use repeatedly, make it a 'Quickstart Module'.</p>
